    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Your Creativity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into <strong>Outside the Blocks</strong>, the ultimate playground for builders and creators who want to express their artistic side in a relaxing, stress-free environment. Forget about objectives and pressure—immerse yourself in the pure joy of creation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/bc368c72f57b252cfe5894ee7b96172e.poster.avif?t=1764615195\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/bc368c72f57b252cfe5894ee7b96172e.webm?t=1764615195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/bc368c72f57b252cfe5894ee7b96172e.mp4?t=1764615195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Innovative Building Tools</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft stunning, one-of-a-kind structures with our unique modular architectural block system. Whether you’re a seasoned designer or a casual creator, our intuitive tools make building a breeze:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Autobuild:</strong> Easily manipulate entire building sections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Storytelling Props &amp; Animated Characters:</strong> Bring your scenes to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adjustable Materials:</strong> Customize object surfaces to fit your vision. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Advanced Layer System:</strong> Achieve precise control over your builds.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/013d41a363a838ed04bd167279acdf73.poster.avif?t=1764615195\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/013d41a363a838ed04bd167279acdf73.webm?t=1764615195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350220/extras/013d41a363a838ed04bd167279acdf73.mp4?t=1764615195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Environment Tools</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your creations to the next level with powerful tools to shape your diorama’s world:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bases &amp; Glass Domes:</strong> Frame your masterpiece in style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nature Elements &amp; Organic Objects:</strong> Add life and vibrancy to your scenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Advanced Terrain Editing:</strong> Shape the ground to match your imagination.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epoxy Resin: </strong>Easily add water levels for stunning aquatic effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weather Conditions &amp; Lighting Schemes:</strong> Set the perfect mood and atmosphere.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Show Off Your Masterpieces</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a built-in <strong>Photo Mode</strong> you can easily capture and share your creations with friends and the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to build, design, and explore your creativity like never before in <strong>Outside the Blocks</strong>—where the only limit is your imagination!</p>",
